## Open Questions

> [!IMPORTANT]
> 1. **Testimonials:** Do you have real client testimonials to use, or should I write realistic placeholder testimonials for now?
> 2. **Client Logos:** Do you have logos of clients/partners, or should I use text-based placeholders?
> 3. **Stats Numbers:** What real numbers should I use? (e.g., projects completed, clients served, years in business)
> 4. **Team Members:** Are there other team members to feature, or should I skip the team section?
> 5. **Pricing:** Do you want pricing tiers or a "Request a Quote" approach?
> 6. **Blog:** Should I create a "Coming Soon" page, or skip entirely for now?
> 7. **Which priorities to implement?** Should I do all 4 priority tiers, or start with Priority 1 & 2 only?

